@startuml
title Saga 分布式事务编排全景

participant "workflow-service\n(Saga Orchestrator)" as wf
participant "order-core" as order
participant "inventory-service" as inv
participant "coupon-service" as coupon
participant "promotion-service" as promo
participant "payment-core" as payment
queue "RocketMQ\n(重试队列)" as mq
database "死信队列\n(人工介入)" as dlq

' ADR-020 CreateOrderSagaDefinition 共 4 步，分两阶段执行：
' 阶段一（本图）: Step 1 createOrder + Step 2 deductInventory
' 阶段二（见 payment-callback.puml）: Step 3 chargePayment + Step 4 confirmOrder

== 正向流程（订单创建 — Saga Step 1+2）==
group 订单创建 Saga
    wf -> order: 1.1 createOrder()
    activate order
    order --> wf: 成功 (订单ID)
    deactivate order

    wf -> inv: 1.2 reserveStock()
    activate inv
    inv --> wf: 成功
    deactivate inv

    wf -> coupon: 1.3 lockCoupon()
    activate coupon
    coupon --> wf: 成功
    deactivate coupon

    wf -> promo: 1.4 updateUsageCount()
    activate promo
    promo --> wf: 成功
    deactivate promo
end

== 补偿流程（任一失败触发）==
note over wf: 如果 1.4 失败，reverse 执行补偿

group Saga 补偿
    wf -> promo: Compensate: 回滚促销用量
    activate promo
    promo --> wf: 成功
    deactivate promo

    wf -> coupon: Compensate: 解锁优惠券
    activate coupon
    coupon --> wf: 成功
    deactivate coupon

    wf -> inv: Compensate: 释放库存
    activate inv
    inv --> wf: 成功
    deactivate inv

    wf -> order: Compensate: 取消订单 (CANCELLED)
    activate order
    order --> wf: 成功
    deactivate order
end

note over wf: 补偿完成 → 订单最终状态 CANCELLED

== 超时与重试机制 ==
group 超时处理
    wf -> inv: 预占库存
    activate inv
    note right: ⏱ 10s 无响应
    wf -> inv: ⚠️ 重试第 1 次
    wf -> inv: ⚠️ 重试第 2 次
    inv --> wf: 失败 (库存不足)
    deactivate inv

    alt 重试耗尽
        wf -> mq: 发送到重试队列
        mq -> dlq: 重试 3 次仍失败 → 死信队列
        note right: ⚠️ 运营人工介入处理
    end
end

== 支付成功 Saga（非补偿型）==
group 支付成功 Saga
    payment -> wf: 支付成功回调
    activate wf
    wf -> order: 2.1 paySuccess() (PENDING_PAY → PAID)
    activate order
    order --> wf: 成功
    deactivate order

    wf -> inv: 2.2 confirmDeduct()
    activate inv
    inv --> wf: 成功
    deactivate inv

    wf -> logistics: 2.3 createFulfillment()
    activate logistics
    logistics --> wf: 成功
    deactivate logistics

    note right: 支付成功不补偿\n失败 → 人工介入 + 对账补偿
    deactivate wf
end

@enduml
